description: This Chainlink VRF top 9% rating Anurak purrs with a rating of 79, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 79, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Box for North, 1 for East, 1 for South, and Leverage for West. Anurak has the personality suit of hodler. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/20791-41163-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
